{"tid":2146901,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個中學最撚on9嘅事 (2)","createTime":"2020-08-09T01:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T13:40:40.000Z","uid":47614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c57eb4b60cbfe904d821fe6ebb2b2f08ee1c254c","tid":2146901,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:46:04.000Z","msg":"繼續 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個po係想討論學校on9政策/文化<br />\n可能講得唔係好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\npost 1: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2140916\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2140916</a>"},{"pid":"9a4b45d574fa8a3ecee8ccd6caad3b6ce477602a","tid":2146901,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T01:47:35.000Z","msg":"不過講下啲on9仔/老師都冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07507d279f4701221290e769719b2f13c06b5bf1","tid":2146901,"uid":353841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:34:45.000Z","msg":"唔俾擺野係櫃桶。<br />\n啲櫃桶都唔知買返來唔俾人用做乜撚野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbadf19bdf561d8388364a5f6cd7664928432cd3","tid":2146901,"uid":117473,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:26:14.000Z","msg":"1. 夏天班房開冷氣熱到好似冇開咁,之後發現Samsung 機可以用紅外線較冷氣。之後較左,我哋課室係全部課室之中最凍,連成日嘅報串撚都唔報我哋偷較冷氣。(後面直接攞屋企remote 較冷氣)<br />\n2. 學校有訂報紙,要搵啲同學去朝早派。派報紙啲人永遠唔洗去早會,晨咁早上課室,較冷氣嘆。冬天又唔洗帶件死人校褸。每個月都有升旗禮,喺高樓層望住啲人企係足球場暴曬。有啲派報紙嘅人成日都遲到,成機入lift扮無事"},{"pid":"e998101a92aa775ad8e974489c60d8e73068a6ce","tid":2146901,"uid":59283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:16:20.000Z","msg":"個同學唔知做咩9 一拳打爆隻窗比人記過<br />\n事後係msn改名做&rdquo;單手打爆玻璃的x&rdquo;+用張爛窗相做頭像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea6c418179143fedf8c5f485922566a21ca8fc4","tid":2146901,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07507d279f4701221290e769719b2f13c06b5bf1","tid":2146901,"uid":353841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:34:45.000Z","msg":"唔俾擺野係櫃桶。<br />\n啲櫃桶都唔知買返來唔俾人用做乜撚野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:29:50.000Z","msg":"咁櫃桶有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係要臨放學前要清走呀"},{"pid":"5923592c0e925b60bd317ae62ad50fa5963a92a9","tid":2146901,"uid":66781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:32:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3038837fb931bb1868b1e293b9b3b4d8e662629c","tid":2146901,"uid":85118,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:32:59.000Z","msg":"Not 文化但都想share<br />\n<br />\n上堂傳紙仔，同個fd傾星期五打邊爐<br />\n點知飛咗落咗地 (我坐第一行)<br />\n俾啊sir 執咗嚟睇<br />\n睇完笑咗笑，但無屌9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a317ad0a650a9de5dfe7f52c2f21aaa2b4dda806","tid":2146901,"uid":190032,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:35:02.000Z","msg":"中六mock嘅事 翻學搭車帶AirPods唔記得除<br />\n個考官話開考先意識到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1123dec4e11a4e684cb294dc3409687a4113955f","tid":2146901,"uid":85118,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:39:27.000Z","msg":"仲有單小一定小二<br />\n<br />\n肥得濟解唔開皮帶<br />\n叫咗fd A入廁格幫我解<br />\n<br />\nFd B以為我地杯9佢定<br />\n係咁喺出面推門<br />\n唔記得我未解到定點我同A喺入面鬥力推返出去<br />\n<br />\n點知成道門甩撚咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66b5c883035d211d08402b02858b7375e4a6f3d","tid":2146901,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07507d279f4701221290e769719b2f13c06b5bf1","tid":2146901,"uid":353841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T02:34:45.000Z","msg":"唔俾擺野係櫃桶。<br />\n啲櫃桶都唔知買返來唔俾人用做乜撚野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"因為有人偷書去賣"},{"pid":"386447d698682c20a21f4cdc141357925407b4f8","tid":2146901,"uid":190032,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:55:52.000Z","msg":"中學唔比着PE衫翻學 一定要帶翻去換<br />\n有個人好晏先入更衣室 夠晒鐘上堂都未換完<br />\n個老師以為齊人鎖左更衣室門<br />\n個傻鳩就比人鎖左成堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf05eb33f8b2992127e8778044a50872f142deac","tid":2146901,"uid":363701,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:07:03.000Z","msg":"試過有次秋季旅行 點完名之後同班friend偷走搭巴士落山去左飲茶<br />\n食完野返喱見仲未走得就去左果到啲小食亭買水槍玩 然後越喱越多人加入戰圈 玩到頭髮都濕晒。我地見啲教畜笑得咁開心 就係水槍到加啲檸檬茶射鳩佢地。<br />\n佢地笑得好開心 仲覺得師生樂也融融<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da79e88f48e97989a04bbc8380d605290a873537","tid":2146901,"uid":66781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:05:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab42d78666e5c40282f4dc453b24305e94bba539","tid":2146901,"uid":236011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:50:46.000Z","msg":"仲有一單 中二個年上數學係分班加分組上嘅 有一次有個同學上堂食糖 跟住個阿sir勁激動咁鬧佢 個同學唔認食糖 個阿sir一路整個I&rsquo;m watching you嘅手勢整咗幾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一路講我明明見到你食㗎 成件事好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb0413dd7bd4fbe6ad05245aa8e91073b4fdc10","tid":2146901,"uid":96154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"以前讀英中，學校逼人訂英文報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a97f03686c561ed9d5ab6de584a506f01cd15ea","tid":2146901,"uid":258502,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T18:26:30.000Z","msg":"係我F.6 臨last day前幾個星期個陣...<br />\n同玩得埋幾個同班同學約左係lunch time 留係班房打邊爐<br />\n，有人帶左個電爐+煲返黎<br />\n係lunch time 前一個小息開始插電制較最細火煮湯底，放係locker 到，有一小段電線出左黎都冇俾老師發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一到lunch time就開餐，搵人出面睇水，老師差唔多巡到 就塞返落locker <br />\n到食完清場，有人帶左檸檬 榨汁 +廁所梘液溝水，入落課室支消毒酒精噴樽((事前有將酒精擺去第二度暫存))之後拎黎噴僻走打邊爐陣除，由頭到尾冇俾人發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加諗返起，真係好L癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nP.s 學校有規矩 話唔俾人係課室食野"},{"pid":"508bf619a28577baf8f2346c6c14f2853ad86c13","tid":2146901,"uid":135081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf05eb33f8b2992127e8778044a50872f142deac","tid":2146901,"uid":363701,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T05:07:03.000Z","msg":"試過有次秋季旅行 點完名之後同班friend偷走搭巴士落山去左飲茶<br />\n食完野返喱見仲未走得就去左果到啲小食亭買水槍玩 然後越喱越多人加入戰圈 玩到頭髮都濕晒。我地見啲教畜笑得咁開心 就係水槍到加啲檸檬茶射鳩佢地。<br />\n佢地笑得好開心 仲覺得師生樂也融融<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T20:17:21.000Z","msg":"我係偷走去咗行山<br />\n俾個班主任急call我返去<br />\n最尾要見校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f781c80d1572859f0904fd1b6fd459eb97f71319","tid":2146901,"uid":54134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e998101a92aa775ad8e974489c60d8e73068a6ce","tid":2146901,"uid":59283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T04:16:20.000Z","msg":"個同學唔知做咩9 一拳打爆隻窗比人記過<br />\n事後係msn改名做&rdquo;單手打爆玻璃的x&rdquo;+用張爛窗相做頭像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T20:19:08.000Z","msg":"屎塔？"},{"pid":"d1457d6bceead9dddc2b6260fb122833c58991cb","tid":2146901,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a97f03686c561ed9d5ab6de584a506f01cd15ea","tid":2146901,"uid":258502,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T18:26:30.000Z","msg":"係我F.6 臨last day前幾個星期個陣...<br />\n同玩得埋幾個同班同學約左係lunch time 留係班房打邊爐<br />\n，有人帶左個電爐+煲返黎<